      "title": "Required run-store files are still untracked and not in the reviewed diff",
      "detail": "The patch now imports `../lib/run-store-ops.js` from the CLI, but `git status` still shows `src/lib/run-store-ops.ts` and `src/tests/run-store-ops.test.ts` as untracked (`??`). That means the reviewed `git diff` does not actually include the new helper or its unit tests, so a clean checkout of this diff will not satisfy acceptance criteria 5 and 8 and can fail to build. Add those files to the patch before landing.",
